        {
            "title": "理想汽車3月份交付新車按年增11.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">理想汽車(02015)公布，在今年3月份交付新車逾4.1萬輛，較去年同期的逾3.66萬輛增加約11.9%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：理想汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251201_FI_source-web_02015-i6-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：理想汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251201_FI_source-web_02015-i6-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：理想汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司表示，隨著產能瓶頸解決，3月份理想i6交付超過2.4萬輛，而全新一代理想L9則預計在第2季上市。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至3底，理想汽車歷史累計交付量已增至超過163.53萬輛。公司在全國已有517家零售中心，覆蓋160個城市；售後維修中心及授權服務中心552家，覆蓋223個城市；在全國已投入使用4057座理想超充站，擁有逾2.24萬個充電樁。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15824207-%e7%90%86%e6%83%b3%e6%b1%bd%e8%bb%8a3%e6%9c%88%e4%bb%bd%e4%ba%a4%e4%bb%98%e6%96%b0%e8%bb%8a%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e11-9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230804_FI_source-web_02015_Li_fb.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-01 17:36:57",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
